import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
plt.scatter(df['Number of Open Accounts'], df['Current Credit Balance'], color='blue')
plt.title('Number of Open Accounts vs Current Credit Balance')
plt.xlabel('Number of Open Accounts')
plt.ylabel('Current Credit Balance')
plt.grid(True)
plt.show()
